$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|...$k$pOh no... This can't be...$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Cool2|What's wrong?$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|I can feel time being distorted.
She draws near.$k$pGullveig has come here from some
distant future.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Should we face her?$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|No. She cannot be defeated.$k$pAll who face her are returned
to nothingness... As I believe
$Nu knows.$k$p$WmMPID_アンナ,ch00_03_Anna_F_Normal,Face_Pain|Then should we hurry and leave
before she's able to find us?$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face|Yes. We must go.$k$p$Sbs1000|

$WmMEID_グルヴェイグ,ch00_47_Gullveig_F_Normal,Face|...$k$p$WmMEID_ヴェロニカ,ch00_04_Veronica2_F_Normal,Face|Halt.$k$pWho are you? What are you doing
in Embla?$k$p$WmMEID_グルヴェイグ,ch00_47_Gullveig_F_Normal,Face|...$k$p$WmMEID_ヴェロニカ,ch00_04_Veronica2_F_Normal,Face|Unknown forces have been
appearing within our borders...$k$pIs this your doing?$k$p$WmMEID_グルヴェイグ,ch00_47_Gullveig_F_Normal,Face|...$k$p$WmMEID_ヴェロニカ,ch00_04_Veronica2_F_Normal,Face|If you deny it, do so. If not, then
I will be—$k$p$WmMEID_グルヴェイグ,ch00_47_Gullveig_F_Normal,Face|Nothing I say to you now will
change the future that comes
for you and your people.$k$pWe will not know peace.$k$p$WmMEID_ヴェロニカ,ch00_04_Veronica2_F_Normal,Face_Anger|I see. In that case...$k$pI will kill you and be done
with this.$k$p$WmMEID_グルヴェイグ,ch00_47_Gullveig_F_Normal,Face|I am the Golden Seer, she who
commands all of time. There is
nothing beyond my sight.$k$pShall I tell you how this fight
will end?$k$p$Sbs150|
